European Stocks Fall as Basic-Resource Companies, Oil and Gas Shares Drop

-- B y   D a v i d   M e r r i t t
-- 
2011-03-09T14:42:38Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-09/european-stocks-fall-as-basic-resource-companies-oil-and-gas-shares-drop.html
European stocks retreated, as
declines by basic-resource and oil and gas shares overshadowed
gains by travel companies.  The benchmark Stoxx Europe 600 Index slid 0.2 percent to
281.18 at 2:42 p.m. in  London , after earlier rising as much as
0.5 percent.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
